	* term/pdf.trm: Always start a new path with a moveto.
	Bug #2930705

	* src/plot2d.c (eval_plots): In generating points for a function plot,
	only x and y were guaranteed to be initialized. Now to be safe we
	initialize all fields.
	Bug #2930705

